quran[5{c,v,t}:
9,107,"kuch aur log hain jinhon ne aik masjid banai iss gharz ke liye ke ( dawat haq ko ) nuqsaan p_hnchayin, aur ( khuda ki bandagi karne ke bajaye ) kufar karen, aur ahal imaan mein phoot dalain, aur ( is bzahir ibadat gaah ko ) uss shakhs ke liye kameen gaah banayen jo is se pehlay khuda aur Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke khilaaf Bar sir pekaar ho chuka hai woh zaroor kasmain kha kha kar kahin ge ke hamara iradah to bhalai ke siwa kisi doosri cheez ka nah tha magar Allah gawah hai ke woh qatee jhutay hain"
9,108,"tum hargiz is imarat mein kharray nah hona jo masjid awwal roz se taqwa par qaim ki gayi thi wohi is ke liye ziyada mozoon hai ke tum is mein ( Ibad t- ke liye ) kharray ho, is mein aisay log hain jo pak rehna pasand karte hain aur Allah ko pakizgee ikhtiyar karne walay hi pasand hain"
9,109,phir tumhara kya khayaal hai ke behtar ensaan woh hai jis ne apni imarat ki bunyaad khuda ke khauf aur is ki Raza ki talab par rakhi ho ya woh jis ne apni imarat aik waadi ki khokhli be Sabaat kagar par uthai aur woh usay le kar seedhi jahannum ki aag mein ja giri? aisay zalim logon ko Allah kabhi seedhi raah nahi dekhata
9,110,"yeh imarat jo unhon ne banai hai, hamesha un ke dilon mein be yakeeni ki jarr bani rahay gi ( jis ke niklny ki ab koi soorat nahi ) bajuz is ke ke un ke dil hi Parah Parah ho jayen Allah nihayat bakhabar aur hakeem o Dana hai"
9,111,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah ne mominoun se un ke nafs aur un ke maal jannat ke badlay khareed liye hain woh Allah ki raah mein lartay aur maartay aur martay hain un se ( jannat ka wada ) Allah ke zimmay aik pukhta wada hai Touraat aur injeel aur quran mein aur kon hai jo Allah se barh kar apne ehad ka poora karne wala ho? pas khusihyan maanao apne is saudey par jo tum ne khuda se chuka liya hai, yahi sab se barri kamyabi hai"
